    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="CH1a0928-start">
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0928_CHANT_001-1a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-03-18T23:38:18.258+09:00">While heaven is bright,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0928_CHANT_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-03-18T23:38:31.662+09:00"> it does not worry that the people are in the dark.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0928_CHANT_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-03-18T23:38:38.991+09:00">While the earth is bountiful,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0928_CHANT_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-03-18T23:39:00.714+09:00">it does not worry that there is insufficiencyamong the people.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0928_CHANT_001-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-03-18T23:39:08.12+09:00">While the sage is potent,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0928_CHANT_001-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-03-18T23:39:14.063+09:00">he does not worry that thepeople are endangered.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0928_CHANT_001-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-03-18T23:39:22.853+09:00">Even though heaven does not worry that the peopleare in the dark,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0928_CHANT_001-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-03-18T23:39:49.328+09:00"> those who open up doors and windows certainly can takefrom [heaven] in order to obtain their own illumination,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0928_CHANT_001-1a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-03-18T23:45:41.747+09:00">though heavendoes nothing.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0928_CHANT_001-1a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-03-18T23:46:05.901+09:00">Even though the earth does not worry that there is insufficiency among the people,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0928_CHANT_001-1a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-03-18T23:46:19.136+09:00">those who chop down trees and cut grasses cancertainly draw from [the earth] in order to obtain their own bounty,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0928_CHANT_001-1a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-03-18T23:46:27.936+09:00">thoughthe earth does nothing.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0928_CHANT_001-1a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-03-18T23:46:37.051+09:00">Even though the sage does not worry that peopleare endangered,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0928_CHANT_001-1a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-03-18T23:47:06.41+09:00">those of the hundred surnames who take the sage as theirstandard from above and harmonize with those below</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0928_CHANT_001-1a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-03-18T23:53:56.539+09:00">can certainly drawfrom [the sage] in order to attain their own security, though the sage does nothing.</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
